❓ Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)
How do I update the menu after an NBA 2K27 patch?When 2K releases an update, they shift memory addresses. You will need to download the latest updated build from the Releases tab to ensure the offsets match the new game version.

Can this be used in online Park or Rec games?NO. Attempting to use memory modifications online will trigger 2K's anti-cheat immediately, resulting in a permanent ban. Keep it strictly offline.

What should I do if the menu doesn't appear?

Ensure you ran the injector as Administrator. 2. Check your Antivirus—Windows Defender frequently false-positives game injectors as malware. You must whitelist the file. 3. Make sure you press F11 after the game fully loads.
Will God Mode work with all positions?Yes. The script dynamically reads your player's position and maxes out the relevant attribute caps, whether you are a 7'3" center or a 6'0" point guard.

Can I unlock badges without corrupting my save file?Yes. The unlocker simply flips progression flags in the game's RAM. It does not overwrite your hard drive save files.

